    74	- `AssistantDefinition` interface is defined and exported from `packages/core/src/index.ts`
    75	- `AssistantRuntime` interface is defined and exported
    76	- `createAssistant` factory is exported; it validates `definition` and throws `AssistantDefinitionError` on invalid input
    77	- `runtime.status()` returns `RuntimeStatus` reflecting `ready`, `startedAt`, `registeredCapabilities`, `registeredSubsystems`, `inFlightHandlers`
    78	- At least one test exercises the full start/stop cycle with a stub relay adapter
    79	- No network calls, no side effects outside in-memory state
    80	- `RelayInboundAdapter` and `RelayOutboundAdapter` interfaces are exported (with `RelayInboundAdapter.onMessage` accepting `InboundMessage` per Contradiction 1 resolution)
