   125	## WF-3: Create and manage sessions
   126	
   127	**Package:** `sessions`
   128	**Depends on:** `docs/specs/v1-sessions-spec.md` (independent of WF-1/WF-2 ŌĆö parallelizable)
   129	**Produces:** `SessionStore`, `Session`, lifecycle transitions, in-memory `SessionStoreAdapter`, error types
   130	**PR scope:** `packages/sessions/src/types.ts`, `packages/sessions/src/sessions.ts`, `packages/sessions/src/sessions.test.ts`
   131	
   132	### Steps
   133	
   134	1. Create a session store: `createSessionStore({ adapter: new InMemorySessionStoreAdapter() })`
   135	2. Call `store.create({ id: uuid(), userId, workspaceId })` ŌĆö returns `Session` with `state: 'created'`, timestamps
   136	3. Call `store.get(sessionId)` ŌĆö returns the same session
   137	4. Call `store.touch(sessionId)` ŌĆö state transitions to `'active'`, `lastActivityAt` updates
   138	5. Call `store.attachSurface(sessionId, surfaceId)` ŌĆö `session.attachedSurfaces` includes the surface id
   139	6. Call `store.detachSurface(sessionId, surfaceId)` ŌĆö `session.attachedSurfaces` no longer includes it (idempotent)
   140	7. Call `store.expire(sessionId)` ŌĆö state transitions to `'expired'`
   141	8. Verify `store.get(unknownId)` returns `null`
   142	9. Verify `store.sweepStale(ttlMs)` transitions active sessions with stale `lastActivityAt` to `'suspended'`
   143	10. Verify illegal transitions throw `SessionStateError` (e.g., `expire` on already-expired session is idempotent per spec; `touch` after `expired` should throw)
   144	
   145	### Acceptance criteria
   146	
   147	- `Session` interface matches spec: `id`, `userId`, `workspaceId?`, `state`, `createdAt`, `lastActivityAt`, `stateChangedAt?`, `attachedSurfaces`, `metadata`
   148	- `SessionState` union type: `'created' | 'active' | 'suspended' | 'expired'`
   149	- `SessionStore` interface fully implemented with `create`, `get`, `find`, `touch`, `attachSurface`, `detachSurface`, `expire`, `sweepStale`, `updateMetadata`
   150	- `createSessionStore` factory exported from `packages/sessions/src/index.ts`
   151	- `InMemorySessionStoreAdapter` exported (or exported as `createInMemorySessionStoreAdapter()`)
   152	- `SessionNotFoundError`, `SessionConflictError`, `SessionStateError` exported
   153	- All lifecycle transitions are tested including stale sweep
   154	- `AffinityResolver` interface exported; default implementation finds most recently active session for a userId
   155	
   156	### Open questions to resolve before coding
   157	
   158	- OQ-1: `sweepStale()` is caller-driven in v1 (no internal timer)
   159	- OQ-4: `AffinityResolver` is passed at call-site to `resolveSession()` utility, not at store level
