   234	
   235	- `core`
   236	- `sessions`
   237	- `surfaces`
   238	- `memory` (v1.1)
   239	- `proactive` (v1.2)
   240	
   241	Keep in Sage:
   242	
   243	- knowledge and workspace-specific prompt behavior
   244	- product-specific follow-up heuristics
   245	- memory retrieval logic (until `@relay-assistant/memory` ships in v1.1)
