   283	
   284	## 5. Dependency Rules
   285	
   286	| Direction | Rule |
   287	|---|---|
   288	| Other packages ŌåÆ core | Allowed. Import types and factory functions only. |
   289	| Core ŌåÆ other packages | Forbidden. Core has no runtime imports from this monorepo. |
   290	| Core ŌåÆ relay foundation | Through adapter interfaces only. Core never imports relay packages. |
   291	| Cloud layer ŌåÆ core | Allowed. Cloud layer may wrap or extend, but core must remain functional without it. |
