   295	## 6. `createAssistant` Factory
   296	
   297	```typescript
   298	export function createAssistant(
   299	  definition: AssistantDefinition,
   300	  adapters: {
   301	    inbound: RelayInboundAdapter;
   302	    outbound: RelayOutboundAdapter;
   303	  },
   304	): AssistantRuntime;
   305	```
   306	
   307	- Validates `definition` structure; throws `AssistantDefinitionError` on invalid input.
   308	- Builds the internal capability dispatch table.
   309	- Wires relay adapters to the internal event loop.
   310	- Does **not** call `onStart` or begin processing; caller must call `runtime.start()`.
