   376	
   377	| Direction | Rule |
   378	|---|---|
   379	| Surfaces ŌåÆ core | Allowed. Import types only (InboundMessage, OutboundEvent). |
   380	| Surfaces ŌåÆ sessions | Allowed. Import Session type for fanout. |
   381	| Surfaces ŌåÆ memory | Forbidden. |
   382	| Surfaces ŌåÆ routing | Forbidden. |
   383	| Surfaces ŌåÆ relay foundation | Forbidden. Relay foundation depends on surfaces, not vice versa. |
   384	| Other packages ŌåÆ surfaces | Allowed. Import SurfaceRegistry, SurfaceConnection types. |
